  "display_fullname": "Incarnate Lore Pet Banished Boss Frigid Beam",
  "display_help": "You focus death energy into both of your fists before unleashing a deadly beam at a target. The affected target and all those within a cone between you suffer cold damage and negative energy damage over time. Additionally, all affected targets lose endurance and have lowered resistance to all damage. Finally, the longer you remain in combat, the more likely you will sap the target's soul, causing them to suffer increased endurance cost for all powers.<br><br><color #fcfc95>Notes: Frigid Beam is unaffected by Range changes.</color><br><br><color #fcfc95>Damage: High.</color><br><color #fcfc95>Recharge: Slow.</color>",
